LABEL: HEADER
QUERY: NULL

LABEL: NUM_REG_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id) from catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_collection_protocol where catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=catissue_collection_protocol.identifier and catissue_collection_protocol.identifier =? and catissue_collection_protocol.activity_status='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'

LABEL: NUM_MALE_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_participant.gender='Male Gender' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_FEMALE_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_participant.gender='Female Gender' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_ALIVE_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_participant.vital_status='Alive' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_DEAD_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_participant.vital_status='Dead'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_CONSENTED_PARTICIPANT
QUERY: select count(DISTINCT catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_consent_tier_response where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier=catissue_consent_tier_response.coll_prot_reg_id and catissue_participant.activity_status='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' and catissue_consent_tier_response.response NOT IN ('Not Specified') and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_WHITE_RACE_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_race where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id=catissue_race.participant_id and catissue_participant.activity_status='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_race.race_name='White'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_ASIAN_RACE_PARTICIPANTS
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_race where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id=catissue_race.participant_id and catissue_participant.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_race.race_name='Asian'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_AME_IND_OR_ALASKA_NATIVE
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_race where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id=catissue_race.participant_id and catissue_participant.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_race.race_name='American Indian or Alaska Native'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_BLACK_OR_AFRICAN_AMERICAN
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_race where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id=catissue_race.participant_id and catissue_participant.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_race.race_name='Black or African American'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_NATIVE_HAWAIIAN_OR_PACIFIC_ISLANDER
QUERY: select count(catissue_participant.identifier)from catissue_participant,catissue_coll_prot_reg,catissue_race where catissue_participant.identifier=catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id and catissue_coll_prot_reg.participant_id=catissue_race.participant_id and catissue_participant.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_race.race_name='Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_COMPLETE_SCG
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier) from catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and  catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen_coll_group.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_status='Complete'

LABEL: NUM_PENDING_SCG
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier) from catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen_coll_group.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_status='Pending'

LABEL: NUM_PENDING_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Pending'

LABEL: NUM_CELL_SPECIMEN_COLLECTED
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catissue_specimen.identifier) FROM catissue_specimen JOIN catissue_specimen_coll_group ON catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier=catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id JOIN catissue_coll_prot_reg ON catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier=catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id AND catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? AND catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected' AND catissue_specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS='Cell'

LABEL: NUM_TISSUE_SPECIMEN_COLLECTED
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catissue_specimen.identifier) FROM catissue_specimen JOIN catissue_specimen_coll_group ON catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier=catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id JOIN catissue_coll_prot_reg ON catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier=catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id AND catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? AND catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected' AND catissue_specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS='Tissue'

LABEL: NUM_FLUID_SPECIMEN_COLLECTED
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catissue_specimen.identifier) FROM catissue_specimen JOIN catissue_specimen_coll_group ON catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier=catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id JOIN catissue_coll_prot_reg ON catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier=catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id AND catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? AND catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected' AND catissue_specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS='Fluid'

LABEL: NUM_MOL_SPECIMEN_COLLECTED
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT catissue_specimen.identifier) FROM catissue_specimen JOIN catissue_specimen_coll_group ON catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier=catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id JOIN catissue_coll_prot_reg ON catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier=catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id AND catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' AND catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? AND catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected' AND catissue_specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS='Molecular'

LABEL: NUM_MALIGNANT_COLL_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.pathological_status='Malignant' and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected'

LABEL: NUM_AVAILABLE_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.available=1 and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected'

LABEL: NUM_COLL_MLGNT_AVAILABLE_CELL_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_cell_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.identifier=catissue_cell_specimen.identifier and catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.pathological_status='Malignant'and catissue_specimen.available=1 and catissue_specimen.available_quantity > 0 and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected'

LABEL: NUM_COLL_MLGNT_AVAILABLE_TISSUE_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_tissue_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.identifier=catissue_tissue_specimen.identifier and  catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.pathological_status='Malignant'and catissue_specimen.available=1 and catissue_specimen.available_quantity >0 and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected'

LABEL: NUM_COLL_MLGNT_AVAI_FLUID_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_fluid_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.identifier=catissue_fluid_specimen.identifier and  catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.pathological_status='Malignant'and catissue_specimen.available=1 and catissue_specimen.available_quantity >0 and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected'

LABEL: NUM_COLL_MLGNT_AVAI_MOL_SPECIMEN
QUERY: select count(catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_molecular_specimen,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.identifier=catissue_molecular_specimen.identifier and  catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_specimen.activity_status='Active'and catissue_coll_prot_reg.activity_status='Active' and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=? and catissue_specimen.pathological_status='Malignant'and catissue_specimen.available=1 and catissue_specimen.available_quantity >0 and catissue_specimen.collection_status='Collected'

LABEL: NUM_DISTRIBUTED_SPECIMENS
QUERY: select count( distinct catissue_specimen.identifier)from catissue_specimen,catissue_distributed_item,catissue_specimen_coll_group,catissue_coll_prot_reg where catissue_specimen.identifier=catissue_distributed_item.specimen_id and catissue_specimen.specimen_collection_group_id=catissue_specimen_coll_group.identifier and catissue_specimen_coll_group.collection_protocol_reg_id=catissue_coll_prot_reg.identifier and catissue_coll_prot_reg.collection_protocol_id=?

LABEL: NUM_USERS
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CATISSUE_USER A WHERE A.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_USERS_ACCESSED_MONTH
QUERY: SELECT (count(distinct(user_id))) FROM catissue_audit_event ae WHERE MONTH(ae.event_timestamp) = MONTH(now()) AND YEAR (ae.event_timestamp) = YEAR(now())

LABEL: NUM_PENDING_USERS
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CATISSUE_USER A WHERE A.ACTIVITY_STATUS = 'Pending' or A.ACTIVITY_STATUS='New'

LABEL: NUM_REPOSITORIES
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CATISSUE_SITE A WHERE A.TYPE LIKE 'Repository' AND A.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_ACTIVE_CP
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CATISSUE_COLLECTION_PROTOCOL B WHERE B.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_ACTIVE_DP
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CATISSUE_DISTRIBUTION_PROTOCOL B WHERE B.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_REG_PARTICIPANTS_SYS
QUERY: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM CATISSUE_PARTICIPANT A WHERE A.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_COLLECTED_SPECIMEN_TOTAL
QUERY: select count(*) from CATISSUE_SPECIMEN specimen where specimen.COLLECTION_STATUS = 'Collected' and specimen.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_COLLECTED_SPECIMEN_MONTH
QUERY: select (count(distinct(cspe.identifier))) from catissue_specimen cspe inner join catissue_specimen_coll_group scg on scg.identifier = cspe.SPECIMEN_COLLECTION_GROUP_ID inner join catissue_coll_prot_reg cpr on cpr.identifier = scg.collection_protocol_reg_id where cspe.collection_status='Collected' and cspe.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active' and MONTH(registration_date) = MONTH(now()) AND YEAR(registration_date) = YEAR(now())

LABEL: NUM_SPECIMENS_BY_FLUID_CLASS_SYS
QUERY: select count(*) from CATISSUE_SPECIMEN specimen where specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS = 'Fluid' and specimen.COLLECTION_STATUS = 'Collected' and specimen.AVAILABLE=1 and specimen.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_SPECIMENS_BY_TISSUE_CLASS_SYS
QUERY: select count(*) from CATISSUE_SPECIMEN specimen where specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS = 'Tissue' and specimen.COLLECTION_STATUS = 'Collected' and specimen.AVAILABLE=1 and specimen.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_SPECIMENS_BY_MOLECULAR_CLASS_SYS
QUERY: select count(*) from CATISSUE_SPECIMEN specimen where specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS = 'Molecular' and specimen.COLLECTION_STATUS = 'Collected' and specimen.AVAILABLE=1 and specimen.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_SPECIMENS_BY_CELL_CLASS_SYS
QUERY: select count(*) from CATISSUE_SPECIMEN specimen where specimen.SPECIMEN_CLASS = 'Cell' and specimen.COLLECTION_STATUS = 'Collected' and specimen.AVAILABLE=1 and specimen.ACTIVITY_STATUS='Active'

LABEL: NUM_PENDING_ORDERS
QUERY: select count(*) from catissue_order where catissue_order.status='Pending'

LABEL: NUM_PROCESSED_ORDER_MONTH
QUERY: select count(*) from catissue_order where catissue_order.status='Completed' and  MONTH(requested_date) = MONTH(now()) AND YEAR(requested_date) =YEAR(now())

LABEL: NUM_SHIPMENT_REQUESTS_MONTH
QUERY: select count(*) from catissue_shipment_request,catissue_base_shipment where catissue_shipment_request.identifier=catissue_base_shipment.identifier and catissue_base_shipment.activity_status='In Progress' and MONTH(created_date) = MONTH(now()) AND YEAR(created_date) =YEAR(now())

LABEL: NUM_SHIPMENT_PROCESSED_MONTH
QUERY: select count(*) from catissue_base_shipment,catissue_shipment where catissue_shipment.identifier=catissue_base_shipment.identifier and catissue_base_shipment.activity_status='Received' and MONTH(send_date) = MONTH(now()) AND YEAR(send_date) =YEAR(now()));
